==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ignitor
<hw>Ig*nit"or</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that
which, produces ignition; especially, a contrivance for igniting the
powder in a torpedo or the like.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>igniter</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ignivomous</ent>⟦br⟧
